<article>
	<h2>Our Story</h2>
	<p>Cozy Corner Cafe has been in business only a for few years in the New England Area. Our goal is to provide you with a place that can satisfy all needs.<br>
	Whether that be a place to get a quick cup of coffee, or have a delicious smoothie bowl or dive into our Gourmet Toast. You can bring work and settle into our atmosphere for hours, or cozy up with a friend for a breakfast/lunch date.<br>
	</p>

	<h2>How We Started</h2>
<p>Tori Palumbo, the owner and creator of Cozy Corner Cafe has had a life long goal of owning her own cafe. She has done her research in order to bring to you a healthy, fun, and fresh menu that will feed your soul. She has made sure to make Cozy Corner an environment where it can not only be a place to get a bite to eat but a place to decompress and escape the realities of a stressful day.<br>
<img src="../images/smoothiebowl.jpg" alt="bowl" style="width:550px;height:300px;"/></p>
<h5>We are super excited for you to come and try our menu and give us feedback on anything that we can do to better our service! Can't wait to see you soon!</h5>

